Package org.neo4j.internal.batchimport.input

Interface Input

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CsvInput, DataGeneratorInput
    public interface Input
    Unifies all data input given to a BatchImporter to allow for more coherent implementations.

      • nodes

        InputIterable nodes​(Collector badCollector)
        Provides all node data for an import.
        Parameters:
        badCollector - for collecting bad entries.
        Returns:
        an InputIterator which will provide all node data for the whole import.

      • relationships

        InputIterable relationships​(Collector badCollector)
        Provides all relationship data for an import.
        Parameters:
        badCollector - for collecting bad entries.
        Returns:
        an InputIterator which will provide all relationship data for the whole import.

      • idType

        IdType idType()
        Returns:
        IdType which matches the type of ids this Input generates. Will get populated by node import and later queried by relationship import to resolve potentially temporary input node ids to actual node ids in the database.

      • groups

        ReadableGroups groups()
        Returns:
        accessor for id groups that this input has.
